		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Another format of text adventure I recall a few SNES games using is like that of those old "Choose Your own Adventure" books; When faced with an important decision, a list of possible choices is presented and the player selects one. 
<br />
<br />This avoids the need for things like text input with keyboards or parsers, but of course all the games had music and graphics to back it up.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
